des:
Here’s a step by step guide:
1. Download our "i-GATE WiFi" app in Google Play;
2. Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
3. Turn on i-GATE WiFi devices and connect them with "i-GATE WiFi" app;
4. Give your devices friendly names;
5. Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
6. Search the Alexa Skills directory for "i-GATE WiFi";
7. Click Enable skill of "i-GATE WiFi", then login with your i-GATE WiFi credentials on the linking page. Your device will be added automatically.
8. Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices;
9. If you register new devices talk to Echo "Alexa, discover devices." to find them;

Here are the voice commands i-GATE WiFi has:

Gate
Alexa, open the gate
Alexa, close the gate
